titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on (+)-Methyl p-{2-hydroxy-3-(isopropylamino) propoxy} hydrocinnamate hydrochloride.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 6/15/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on (+)-methyl p-(2-hydroxy-3-(isopropylamino) propoxy) hydrocinnamate hydrochloride.
